definition.value: An isochromane that is mellein bearing a methoxy substituent at position 6.
A dicarboxylic acid that is succinic acid substituted by a acetamidomethylidene group at position 2.
An amino alcohol that is propanol substituted by 1H-imidazol-4-yl group at position 3 and an amino group at position 2 (the 2S stereoisomer).
